		<title type="html"><![CDATA[Adult Lib - run old Löve code with the current Löve version]]></title>

		
		<content type="html" xml:base="http://love2d.org/forums/viewtopic.php?p=15727#p15727"><![CDATA[
Here is the original post: <a href="http://forum.freegamedev.net/viewtopic.php?f=20&amp;t=363&amp;p=4193" class="postlink">http://forum.freegamedev.net/viewtopic. ... 363&amp;p=4193</a><br><br>A small lib to run old löve code with the current version. Currently it only supports<br>0.5 -&gt; 0.6.2.<br><br>You can find it under: <a href="http://ghoulsblade.schattenkind.net/files/adult.lua" class="postlink">http://ghoulsblade.schattenkind.net/files/adult.lua</a><br><br>How to use:<br>* Take your 0.5 code and include adult in the first line of your main.lua<br>* Then call adult.grow ("0.5")<br>* If you are lucky enough you will see your game <img class="smilies" src="http://love2d.org/forums/images/smilies/ms-smile.png" width="16" height="16" alt=":)" title="Smile"><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://love2d.org/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=74">hagish</a> — Fri Jun 04, 2010 1:03 pm</p><hr />
